{"tid":2126951,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［卿姐__之吻］林卓廷報名競逐連任 劉慧卿隔罩獻吻支持","createTime":"2020-07-27T05:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T07:29:12.000Z","uid":22556,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0f9309509a2bac7b074eb1d6a4a248f00ac6d4a1","tid":2126951,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:52:32.000Z","msg":"分別循新東及九東爭取連任的民主黨立法會議員林卓廷及胡志偉，今天先後報名競逐連任，獲民主黨前主席劉慧卿隔罩獻吻、祝福順利「冧莊」的林卓廷按民主黨早前決議，簽署確認書；胡志偉則決定不簽確認書，胡指：「簽定唔簽都唔係決定性因素，呢個係（選管會主席）馮驊講嘅」。兩人均斥政府不應借疫推遲選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/OOIL2DDBGCUDCQIY3X7S6QNKUM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FOOIL2DDBGCUDCQIY3X7S6QNKUM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx8VJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=462e3a0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200727%2FOOIL2DDBGCUDCQIY3X7S6QNKUM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6603ee88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200727/OOIL2DDBGCUDCQIY3X7S6QNKUM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"774cdfafb531172e166797107dc9d1faf32f1f0e","tid":2126951,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:56:32.000Z","msg":"口罩最污糟最多毒就係外面個層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a38fdc6b6c038eaa9b2972eabeec73369f9acf","tid":2126951,"uid":8014,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T05:57:10.000Z","msg":"cls 有無常識 口罩外面多菌到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj